  - UI: key metrics cards (items per hour, avg review time, total items, etc.)
- ItemDetailLink
  - Small utility component to navigate to a detailed audit item view
- DataAdapter / Hooks
  - useReviewQueueData: fetch queue data, apply client-side guards, expose data safely
  - useBulkExport: prepare and trigger export (CSV/PDF) with proper null-safe handling
